The Badminton Asia Championships 2022 took place between April 26 and May 1 in Muntinlupa, suburban Manila, Philippines. Winners Men's singles: Lee Zii Jia of Malaysia Women's singles: Wang Zhiyi of China Men's doubles: Pramudya Kusumawardana and Yeremia Erich Yoche Yacob Rambitan of Indonesia Women's doubles: Chen Qingchen and Jia Yifan of China Mixed doubles: Zheng Siwei and Huang Yaqiong of China